May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]: GUIDANCE FOR YOUR MESSAGE:
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]: - Weave together insights from multiple domains (e.g., sleep + activity + energy) in a single message.
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]: - Include positive signals and good news alongside concerns (e.g., 'Home energy is looking great, AND let's check on sleep').
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]: - Regular check-ins on routine topics are welcome — you don't need to wait for urgent issues.
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]: - A balanced message that mentions both strengths and areas to focus on is more supportive than doom-focused.
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]: - ALWAYS include specific numbers and metrics instead of vague language:
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]:   - Say '6.4k steps' not 'good activity'
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]:   - Say '25.8°C' not 'a bit warm'
