May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]:   - Say '35 active minutes' not 'some exercise'
May 13 05:45:27 ip-172-31-27-185 lumie-api[877006]: - Show the actual data from the skill results in your message.
